<inglise> CHAPTER VI SUPERVISORY AUTHORITY AND WORKING PARTY ON THE PROTECTION OF INDIVIDUALS WITH REGARD TO THE PROCESSING OF PERSONAL DATA </inglise>
<eesti> VI PEAT&Uuml;KK J&Auml;RELEVALVEASUTUS JA T&Ouml;&Ouml;R&Uuml;HM &Uuml;KSIKISIKUTE KAITSEKS SEOSES ISIKUANDMETE T&Ouml;&Ouml;TLEMISEGA </eesti>
<inglise> Article 28 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 28 </eesti>
<inglise> Supervisory authority </inglise>
<eesti> J&auml;relevalveasutus </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Each Member State shall provide that one or more public authorities are responsible for monitoring the application within its territory of the provisions adopted by the Member States pursuant to this Directive. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga liikmesriik n&auml;eb ette &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitu riigiasutust, et teostada j&auml;relevalvet tema territooriumil k&auml;esoleva direktiivi kohaselt vastuv&otilde;etud s&auml;tete kohaldamise &uuml;le. </eesti>
<inglise> These authorities shall act with complete independence in exercising the functions entrusted to them. </inglise>
